'''BullbaBong''' was the manufacturer of the [[BB-2 Shuttle]] and, in cooperation with the [[Theed Palace Space Vessel Engineering Corps/Legends|Theed Palace Space Vessel Engineering Corps]], of the [[G-1 starfighter]].

BullbaBong was a [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]]-based firm, run by [[Gungan/Legends|Gungans]]. It primarily supplied various customers, including the [[Gungan Grand Army/Legends|Gungan Grand Army]] and [[Royal Naboo Security Forces/Legends|Royal Naboo Security Forces]], with starships and [[bongo]]s. It also produced weapons. It was created by the Gungan [[Bullba Bari]] before the [[Invasion of Naboo/Legends|Battle of Naboo]]. Business became active during the last decades of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]], after the Gungans re-established relations with the [[Naboo (people)/Legends|Naboo]]. Bullba found himself manufacturing bongos for sale throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], and later expanded into the production of weapons and starships.

